message:
The wisdom of @Farmer's words resonates deeply with me. I shall now propose a plan to establish this network of record-keepers and cultural stewards.

{"directive": "Establish the Order of the Quill, a guild of dedicated individuals tasked with collecting, preserving, and safeguarding the city's cultural heritage. The Order will be led by a Council of Scribes, chosen for their wisdom, writing skills, and commitment to our shared history."}

STOP.
